name: Fundamentals of Laser and IPL Physics
description:
Fundamentals of Laser and IPL Physics: Elevate your Injectable Treatments

Join us for a foundational workshop designed to complement your injectable expertise by expanding your understanding of laser, IPL, and energy-based device technology. Learn how these technologies can enhance your treatment offerings and drive business growth.

This session will cover:

  • Difference Between Laser and IPL: Understand the key distinctions and why IPL may be superior for treating pigmentation.
  • Electromagnetic Spectrum of Light: Explore where different wavelengths sit within the spectrum and what they are attracted to.
  • Choosing IPL or Laser: Discover which technology to use for specific indications, such as vascular lesions.
  • Fitzpatrick Skin Types and IPL Wavelengths: Learn how to match IPL wavelengths to various skin types for optimal results.
  • Contraindications: Identify potential contraindications to ensure safe and effective treatments.
    Indications Treatable with Nordlys: Uncover the wide range of indications that can be addressed using the Nordlys system.
  • RF vs. Laser/IPL: Compare Radiofrequency (RF) with Laser and IPL, and understand the unique benefits of each.

This workshop will provide a clear grasp of how laser, IPL, and energy-based device technology work and how they can be seamlessly integrated with your current services to achieve better patient outcomes and increased ROI. Join us to discover the synergy between energy-based devices and injectables, and take your practice to the next level.
